title: Glamorous 3 Bed in Northwest Austin
posting_body: ['Once you make this your home, life hums along beautifully.', 'Expansive three-bedroom apartment home filled with sleek finishes, plentiful storage, and extra details — the kind that heighten your comfort and maximize your convenience.', 'Amenities are specially designed to help you retreat and recharge, whether you sweat it out, swim it off, or just lay back and take it all in.', 'Your furry fam is priority too, with a dog park and wash station at the ready.', 'This home and neighborhood embodies North Austin’s casual charm and modern flair, so enjoy the vibe.', 'Decadent dining nearby, as well as an elaborate array of popular stores.', 'It’s all for you.', 'The forecast for your life here is looking really good!', 'Move on it!', 'Text 2I0-355-7852', 'Christena Barry - award Winning Locator & Realtor', 'Spirit Real Estate Group', 'ID:  119', '*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.', '*Prices, availability, & specials subject to change.']
